{"data":[{"name":"102:1","price":"1. Bermegah-megahan telah melalaikan kalian,*(923)","arabic":"أَلۡهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6169,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"*923). Bermegah-megahan dalam soal banyak anak, harta, pengikut, kemuliaan dan sebagainya, telah melalaikan kalian dari ketaatan kepada Allah.","lang":"id"},{"name":"102:2","price":"2. sampai kamu masuk ke dalam kubur.","arabic":"حَتَّىٰ زُرۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَقَابِرَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6170,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"102:3","price":"3. Sekali-kali tidak! Kelak kalian akan mengetahui (akibat perbuatan kalian itu).","arabic":"كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6171,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"102:4","price":"4. Kemudian sekali-kali tidak! Kelak kalian akan mengetahui.","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6172,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"102:5","price":"5. Sekali-kali tidak! Sekiranya kalian mengetahui dengan pasti,","arabic":"كَلَّا لَوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عِلۡمَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6173,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"102:6","price":"6. niscaya kalian benar-benar akan melihat neraka Jahim.","arabic":"لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6174,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"102:7","price":"7. Kemudian kalian benar-benar akan melihatnya dengan mata kepala sendiri.","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيۡنَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6175,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"102:8","price":"8. Kemudian kamu benar-benar akan ditanya pada hari itu tentang kenikmatan (yang megah di dunia itu).","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتُسۡـَٔلُنَّ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6176,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"}],"chapter":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur","Chapter At-Takathur","Takathur","Surah Takathur","Chapter Takathur","At Takathur","Surah At Takathur","Chapter At Takathur","Surah 102","Chapter 102","The Rivalry","التكاثر"]}